==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Moniment
<hw>Mon"i*ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>monimentum</ets>, <ets>monumentum</ets>. See
<er>Monument</er>.]</ety> <def>Something to preserve memory; a reminder;
a monument; hence, a mark; an image; a superscription; a record.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

